---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Partner - Universities">
  <Navigation />
  <main>
    <section class="partner-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>partner with us: universities</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="universities-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">
          <h2>why partner with the tech bros</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">We work with universities to help technical women move from theory to practice.</p>
          <p>Our programmes and events expose students and researchers to startup thinking, technical entrepreneurship, and real-world company building, without assuming prior founder experience.</p>
          
          <h3>we partner with:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Departments</li>
            <li>Enterprise teams</li>
            <li>Student societies</li>
            <li>Innovation hubs</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>what partnership looks like</h2>
          <p>We collaborate on hands-on, educational events that complement academic learning.</p>
          
          <h3>typical formats include:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Startup weekends</li>
            <li>Hackathons</li>
            <li>Founder workshops and panels</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We bring external perspective, industry context, and a strong peer cohort.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="spotlight-hero-image">
      <img src="/partner/unit-m-startup-weekend-hero.jpg" alt="Unit M Startup Weekend" />
    </div>

    <section class="spotlight-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="spotlight-content">
          <div class="spotlight-images-left">
            <img src="/partner/unit-m-1.jpg" alt="Unit M Startup Weekend" />
            <img src="/partner/unit-m-2.jpg" alt="Unit M Startup Weekend" />
            <img src="/partner/unit-m-3.jpg" alt="Unit M Startup Weekend" />
          </div>
          <div class="spotlight-text-column">
            <h2>spotlight: unit m startup weekend</h2>
            <p>We partnered with Unit M at the University of Manchester to run a startup weekend designed for technical women exploring entrepreneurship.</p>
            <p>The focus was on:</p>
            <ul class="partner-list">
              <li>Practical company-building skills</li>
              <li>Team formation and collaboration</li>
              <li>Exposure to founders and operators</li>
            </ul>
            <p>The event supported students and early-career researchers in seeing entrepreneurship as a realistic and accessible path.</p>
            
            <div class="spotlight-stats">
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">4.7 / 5</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">Average event rating</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">80%</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">Met potential co-founders</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">93%</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">More likely to start a company</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="spotlight-quotes">
              <blockquote>Thank you so much for organising this! I've left with such a desire to actually take action on ideas I have after seeing how much I could do in just a day! We were staying up late, waking up at 5, working non stop but it didn't feel like work at all. Also was amazing to meet so many cool women!!</blockquote>
              <blockquote>I think the presentations were SO SO helpful because they really gave us a foundation of the basics from scratch. I think I left with a much more informed and confident mindset. I think even if business basics are available on the internet, the whole investor/vc angle is near impossible for newcomers to find. Really really loved that!</blockquote>
              <blockquote>Seeing how quickly we can create an idea from nothing in such a short amount of time and building something with my teammate and feeling passionate about it and learning as we went.</blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="universities-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">

          <h2>who should get in touch</h2>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>University departments with funding for enterprise initiatives</li>
            <li>Innovation and commercialisation teams</li>
            <li>Student societies looking to run high-quality technical events</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We tailor each partnership to the audience and learning goals.</p>
          <p>If you want to give technical women a clearer path from university to startup, we'd love to work with you.</p>

          <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <a href="mailto:team@thetechbros.io" class="btn">Start a Conversation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .partner-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .universities-partner {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .partner-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .partner-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .partner-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .partner-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .partner-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .partner-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .partner-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .partner-list li::before {
    content: 'â†’';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .spotlight-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-text-column h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spotlight-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes blockquote {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-text-column {
      order: 1;
    }

    .spotlight-images-left {
      order: 2;
    }

    .spotlight-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
